{"obj_edit_time":"1769154688","blocks":[{"block_id":"B8CLdepQEoXPOdxaWVWjUh9Tp3g","block_type":1,"children":["doxjpOy5zdkwTghPplSi46JYo6f","doxjpihcCQqMiJOvi5lZttid7Pe","doxjpHV7YI96wQ7wxmOyQObjK7f","doxjpDMkqV5OeQqcF6nQ7X5W5HN","doxjp5mk7f1wthiTKyUpxTZyTTd","doxjpoMBvmntXFlruHIE2X55GZb","doxjpmAfJgvHb8WiuWqUNctt0le","doxjpka1RWUMoLUdPt5bs9ejZcd","doxjpeLM5yFU0vhSArBdBrfQcDe","doxjpOdt099ht46pONqll7iAruh","doxjpxcySwTSN9oqoSQu3uKWVqb","doxjpxMIP9Jk4nW8DBdxfsorcwb","doxjpjFtj8KlEKvcpGB0268OUse","doxjpNx8EgKjhdtL6btd8snqOKb"],"page":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"业务介绍","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1}},"parent_id":""},{"block_id":"doxjpOy5zdkwTghPplSi46JYo6f","block_type":14,"code":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"slug: JIVJwdJCMiZEzGktdYWcjWrNnuf\ntitle: 业务介绍\n","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}},{"text_run":{"content":"sidebar_position: 0","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"language":67,"wrap":false}},"parent_id":"B8CLdepQEoXPOdxaWVWjUh9Tp3g"},{"block_id":"doxjpihcCQqMiJOvi5lZttid7Pe","block_type":3,"heading1":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"业务介绍","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}},"parent_id":"B8CLdepQEoXPOdxaWVWjUh9Tp3g"},{"block_id":"doxjpHV7YI96wQ7wxmOyQObjK7f","block_type":3,"heading1":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"概述","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}},"parent_id":"B8CLdepQEoXPOdxaWVWjUh9Tp3g"},{"block_id":"doxjpDMkqV5OeQqcF6nQ7X5W5HN","block_type":2,"parent_id":"B8CLdepQEoXPOdxaWVWjUh9Tp3g","text":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"在证券市场，公募基金和私募基金是投资者广泛使用的两种主要投资工具。","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}}},{"block_id":"doxjp5mk7f1wthiTKyUpxTZyTTd","block_type":2,"parent_id":"B8CLdepQEoXPOdxaWVWjUh9Tp3g","text":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"公募基金由基金公司发行，向公众开放购买和赎回。这种基金的投资门槛相对较低，投资者可以通过证券交易所或基金销售机构购买。公募基金由专业的基金经理团队管理，投资者可以通过购买基金份额间接投资于股票、债券等资产，实现资产多样化和专业化管理。相对而言，私募基金则向特定投资者发行，投资门槛较高，且购买流程相对复杂。这种基金的运作方式更为灵活，通常包含更多的投资策略和市场环境，适用于机构投资者或个人高净值投资者。","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}}},{"block_id":"doxjpoMBvmntXFlruHIE2X55GZb","block_type":2,"parent_id":"B8CLdepQEoXPOdxaWVWjUh9Tp3g","text":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"投资者参与基金投资的原因包括多方面考量。首先，基金投资可以帮助投资者分散风险。通过将资金投资于不同的资产类别和行业，投资者可以降低单一投资的风险，实现更稳健的投资组合。其次，基金由专业的基金经理团队管理，他们根据市场状况和基金的投资目标进行资产配置和交易，为投资者获取最佳回报。这种专业的管理可以减轻投资者的管理压力，并提高投资的效率和收益率。此外，购买基金相对简单方便，无需直接购买和管理股票或债券，基金公司会代为管理，为投资者提供了便利性和灵活性。","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}}},{"block_id":"doxjpmAfJgvHb8WiuWqUNctt0le","block_type":2,"parent_id":"B8CLdepQEoXPOdxaWVWjUh9Tp3g","text":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"综上所述，基金投资为投资者提供了多样化、专业化的投资选择，使他们能够轻松参与市场并获得相应的投资回报。无论是公募基金还是私募基金，投资者都可以根据自身的需求和风险偏好选择适合的投资产品，并通过简单的购买和赎回流程参与市场，实现长期财富增长的目标。","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}}},{"block_id":"doxjpka1RWUMoLUdPt5bs9ejZcd","block_type":3,"heading1":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"基金交易步骤","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}},"parent_id":"B8CLdepQEoXPOdxaWVWjUh9Tp3g"},{"block_id":"doxjpeLM5yFU0vhSArBdBrfQcDe","block_type":2,"parent_id":"B8CLdepQEoXPOdxaWVWjUh9Tp3g","text":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"在基金交易过程中，券商主要执行以下关键步骤：","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}}},{"block_id":"doxjpOdt099ht46pONqll7iAruh","block_type":13,"children":["doxjpRVvPOs36BSqlzECVFrmv1d"],"ordered":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"接受投资者的申购和赎回指令：客户在终端提交基金的申购和赎回的申请，券商需要接收客户指令同时冻结资金，根据业务规则汇总客户申赎的订单，生成基金文件。","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}},"parent_id":"B8CLdepQEoXPOdxaWVWjUh9Tp3g"},{"block_id":"doxjpRVvPOs36BSqlzECVFrmv1d","block_type":13,"ordered":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"基金下单的方式，不仅可以从投资者使用的终端进行下单，还支持通过基金后台进行下单。","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}},"parent_id":"doxjpOdt099ht46pONqll7iAruh"},{"block_id":"doxjpxcySwTSN9oqoSQu3uKWVqb","block_type":13,"ordered":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"提交基金文件至上手，等待基金公司确认：操作人员在基金管理后台核对生成的基金订单，将申赎数据发送给上手，等待基金公司返回份额和金额信息。","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}},"parent_id":"B8CLdepQEoXPOdxaWVWjUh9Tp3g"},{"block_id":"doxjpxMIP9Jk4nW8DBdxfsorcwb","block_type":13,"ordered":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"回填订单数据：收到基金公司文件，回填基金净值、申购份额、赎回金额等信息，并核对确认。","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}},"parent_id":"B8CLdepQEoXPOdxaWVWjUh9Tp3g"},{"block_id":"doxjpjFtj8KlEKvcpGB0268OUse","block_type":13,"ordered":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"申赎交割：人工/自动进行申购交割、赎回货交割、赎回钱交割，系统根据申购订单扣取客户资金，增加客户的基金份额持仓；根据赎回订单扣取客户份额，返回客户资金。","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}},"parent_id":"B8CLdepQEoXPOdxaWVWjUh9Tp3g"},{"block_id":"doxjpNx8EgKjhdtL6btd8snqOKb","block_type":13,"ordered":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"完成交割，通知客户：后台人员将通过银行与基金託管人交收资金，生成基金交易结单发送至客户。","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}},"parent_id":"B8CLdepQEoXPOdxaWVWjUh9Tp3g"}]}